            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> Caesar divi Traiani <lb n="2"/>Parthici <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> divi Nervae <expan><abbr>nep</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Traianus Hadrianus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potesta</abbr><ex>te</ex></expan> XI <lb n="5"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> III munificentia sua <lb n="6"/>templum Deae Cuprae restituit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: 10.12.126 - 9.12.127 n. Chr. (Hadrian zum 11. Mal Inhaber der tribunizischen Amtsgewalt).</p>
